title: Slimming World - March/April 2016
description:
English | 132 pages | PDF | 57.8 MB

If you want to find out how to become a successful slimmer, then Slimming World magazine offers great ideas, expert advice and news and features on weight loss. It's packed with delicious recipes and celebrity features, plus fashion and beauty tips. This health and fitness magazine is also the perfect source of inspiration, with dozens of accounts from real slimmers of all ages and weights, detailing and sharing their weight loss journey with you
